dsDescriptionValue.value:
This unit was presented at the beginning of each session. It asked Rs to indicate on a 0-100 scale how do you feel right now. (Note: this question was also asked at the end of the session. Those data are in WRAP.) Then Rs were asked to describe the best thing that had happened this week and the worst thing that had happened. They were asked whether anything else out of the ordinary had happened and if so, were asked to describe it. Lastly, they were asked whether they had been ill in the last week and if yes, were asked to briefly describe their illness.

No standard scoring.
